sentences.english: Her Life Line is a green ocean-plant, forest.
sentences.chinese: 她的生命线是绿色的海洋草木，森林。

sentences.english: The road winds through the forest.
Billions years ago, human had moved from ocean to land and dominated the earth;
sentences.chinese: 亿万年后人从陆地走向森林，选择水岸。

sentences.english: The guide misled the tourists in the woods.
sentences.chinese: 向导在森林里给旅游者带错了路。

sentences.english: I believe there is no way out of this forest.
sentences.chinese: 我相信没有戮由以从这森林走出去。

sentences.english: There is no solution to the question of climate change without forestry.
sentences.chinese: 如果不关注森林，那么气候变化问题就是无法解决的。

sentences.english: With more forests being destoryed, huge quantities of good earth are washed away each year.
sentences.chinese: 由于更多森林被破坏，每年有大量的好土壤流失掉了。

sentences.english: They believe themselves to be descendants of the Great Tree, a sacred tree in the forests.
sentences.chinese: 他们相信自己是森林里的一棵圣树“大树”的子孙。

sentences.english: Behind the tip of the A, behind the plateau of Mont -Saint-Jean, is the forest of Soignes.
sentences.chinese: 在A字的尖顶和圣约翰山高地后面的，是索瓦宁森林。

sentences.english: Encourage them to integrate forests into their publicity or philanthropic work.
sentences.chinese: 鼓励他们将森林问题纳入其宣传或慈善工作。

sentences.english: This flitting cheerfulness was always at the farther extremity of some long vista through the forest.
sentences.chinese: 这种转瞬即逝的欢悦总是出现在森林纵深处。

sentences.english: Paul Konchesky has gone out on loan to Nottingham Forest.
sentences.chinese: 孔雀已经租借给了诺丁汉森林。

sentences.english: At the edge of the forest, behind the dunes, I set up my small tarp.
sentences.chinese: 在边缘的森林，背后的沙丘，我设立了我的小篷布。

sentences.english: The natural forest conversation project is an important guarantee for sustainable forest development.
sentences.chinese: 天然林保护工程是森林可持续发展的重要保证。

sentences.english: In fact, we heard that kid is right here in the jungle.
sentences.chinese: 实际上，我们听说那个孩子就正好在森林里。

sentences.english: A little rabbit is picking mushrooms in a forest. A wolf is coming. He is very hungry.
sentences.chinese: 一只小兔子正在森林里采蘑菇，一只狼来了，他很饿。
